@NODE "Project->Buffer Size" "Project->Buffer Size"
@next "Project->Highlight"
@prev "Project->Export"
@TOC "Project"
@Keywords "Changing the buffer size of a project."
Menu:	@{b}Project@{ub}
Item:	@{b}Buffer Size@{ub}

@{b}Function@{ub}
  Changes the current project's buffer size.

@{b}Notes@{ub}
  This operation is not undoable.  Reducing the buffer size will permanently discard areas.  Salvaging these lost parts is sometimes possible.  To attempt this: 1) Enlarge the buffer to original size, 2) Select redo multiple times.
@ENDNODE
